BUSINESS RISK MANAGEMENT ANALYST - OIL & GAS -
Required for a leading Oil & Gas Group CO. in Abudhabi, on DIRECT HIRE .
Duties :
Provides consultation on Business Risk Management (BRM), facilitates workshops and application of BRM techniniques, ad-hoc risk analysis projects and other selected strategic activities as required.
Desired Candidate Profile
Bachelor Degree in Business Administration or equivalent, Preferably a relevant professional qualification in BRM / ERM.
5-6 Years exp. in auditing or risk management - preferably within Oil & Gas Industry.
Ability to think strategically with a high level of understanding business process.
Excellent presentation and communication skills.
Proficient in English.
Thanks & Regards
